comment: Walker (MIA) affects Clarkson's (LAL) RSBQ as he comes across the court.
Whiteside (MIA) is standing in the restricted area when Clarkson (LAL) drives to the rim.
RHH shows Ellington (LAL) fall on and then grab Wade's (MIA) arm as he tries to pass.
Hill (LAL) sets the screen on Dragic (MIA) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Wade (MIA) makes slight contact with Clarkson's (LAL) arm after the ball is released, but does not affect his ability to follow-through.
Contact by Hill (LAL) with Whiteside (MIA) is part of his effort to reach for the loose ball.
R-Slash shows Clarkson (LAL) make contact with Whiteside's (MIA) arm that affects his ability to move freely.
